These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-1::.
House: modern, colonial, craftsman
3 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, rat
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the modern house and the owner of the ferret##7
2. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |
| House   | craftsman | colonial | modern |
| Pet           | ferret  | rat     | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bongani, oliveros
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, tram, van
1. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
2. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the oliveros-smoker and the person driving the tram##7
3. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |
| Cigar   | bongani | ritmeester | oliveros |
| Transport     | tram       | van     | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, water
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, zombie, horror
1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the person drinking coffee and the person watching disaster movies##7
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage    | coffee | mirinda | water  |
| Movie-Genre   | horror  | zombie  | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-4::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, havana, baccarat
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, comedy, time-travel
1. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere between the person watching time-travel movies and the havana-smoker##7
2. the person watching comedy movies is not the old-henry-smoker##6
3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |        2        |      3      |
| Cigar           | havana | old-henry | baccarat     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | action          | time-travel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, hip-hop, salsa
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: thriller, family, western
1. the person watching family movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the fan of hip-hop##7
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | salsa     | hip-hop   |
| Movie-Genre     | western | family | thriller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-6::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, jazz, reggae
There 3 different types of food: kale, banana, watermelon
1. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
2. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person eating kale##5
3. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
4. the fan of jazz is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the fan of blues##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | jazz     | blues     |
| Food   | watermelon | banana | kale |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-7::.
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, lemon, pomegranate
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the person who's sport is badminton##7
3. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |     3      |
| Food     | pomegranate       | lemon      | grapefruit       |
| Sport   | badminton | skateboarding | basketball |

