.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-8::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, baking, hiking
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: mystery, sports, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
2. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person who's hobby is baking##7
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby           | hiking | board-games  | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | mystery | sports      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-9::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, december, august
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, manager, teacher
1. the teacher is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
2. the manager is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the doctor is somewhere between the manager and the person who's birthday is in december##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | december | august | june   |
| Job     | teacher    | doctor  | manager |

