.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, sprite
3 different games are played: snooker, monopoly, whist
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person playing whist is the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person playing monopoly##7

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | milk   | sprite    | coffee |
| Game      | whist | snooker | monopoly |

