.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, september, october
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in march##7
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who's hobby is traveling##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Hobby         | traveling | fishing | rock-climbing |
| Birthday   | september    | october    | march         |

