.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-15::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, turtle
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, aconite, daisy
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the person who growsaconite##7
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Pet     | turtle  | bird       | mouse    |
| Flower   | daffodil | daisy | aconite |

