.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-16::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, peach, potato
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, balloon-flower, begonia
1. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person eating potato##5
2. the person eating potato is the person eating potato##1
3. the person eating peach is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the person who growspoppy##7
4. the person who growspoppy is the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | potato | peach     | avocado   |
| Flower   | begonia   | balloon-flower | poppy |

