.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-7-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, june, september
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, engineer, entrepreneur
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the analyst##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the engineer##7
3. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the engineer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2    |      3      |
| Birthday   | june      | september     | december |
| Job        | entrepreneur | analyst | engineer    |

 